//local category LOCAL
// first place. Location of Durgapur Durgapur is located about 168 KM from Kolkata. The National Highway -2 ( G.T. Road) passes through Durgapur. Durgapur lies in 23.29 N Latitude 87.19 E Longitude. Durgapur is well connected by Indian Railways. Durgapur is also connected with Kolkata by SBSTC buses and private buses. Many VOLVO buses also ply regularly through Durgapur and Kolkata.
// second place. City Centre City-Centre as the name suggest is grooming to become the heart of the city. It is well connected with each and every buses in Durgapur. Now a no of shopping malls arcades and a Cineplex restaurants has grown in the area making it one of the most popular hangout for the youngsters. Various business establishment has opened their offices in City-Centre. All banks have opened the offices and many new are opening there branches in City-centre. Besides City-Centre also boasts of well planned housing complex. From Bengal-Ambuja to various other players have build housing complex in City-Centre Hotel like Peerless Inn, Pathik, Luxor are available in there. The Troika Park, Deer Park, Srijony-Art Gallery, Science Energy Park add to the list of visiting spots in CITY-CENTRE.
// third place. Bidhan Nagar Bidhan Nagar is one of the posh area in Durgapur. It has well planned and modern Housing Complexes. The greenery look and the quiet ambience of the area has its attraction to housing Complex. Many management Institutes has its branches here. The new engineering College, Schools are coming up in the area. The state govt. hospital-Bidhannagar( S.D.) ,E.S.I. Hospital, Dental research and now The Mission Hospital with most modern technology and equipment has grown the area into a medical hub.
// fourth place. Benachity It is the oldest business Area in Durgapur. It is about 3 Km in length with shops in both sides. It is basically small merchandise and whole sell setup business, not the mall type setup. But it is a huge commercial area of Durgapur, all banks in Durgapur have its branches in Benachity. Recently Benachity is also changing its image and now the old shops are getting changed to new multi storey building. Now large show-rooms of every multinational branded company are coming up. Benachity is well connected with each and every buses that ply on Durgapur. The only problem that Benachity has is its parking problem. The streets are very congested and shoppers have often problem in parking their vehicles. The administration is looking after the matter and soon a solution will emerge for the betterment of Durgapur's oldest business establishment- BENACHITY
